author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
In this edition of Marvel Recap, explore the complicated history of Yelena Belova, the successor to Natasha Romanoff, A.K.A. Black Widow.  From battling dino-mutants to becoming a Hydra super weapon, Yelena has quite the story to tell. Learn all about her covert history with the Soviet Union and her struggle to become a superior replacement to her infamous predecessor. Hydra, A.I.M., The Blood Hunters, S.H.I.E.L.D., The Thunderbolts, Yelena has spied for just about everyone... but where do her true loyalties lie?  Find out by watching this top-secret explainer video... just keep it on the QT.
